org.nd4j.adapters

Interface InferenceAdapter<I,O>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of the Input for the model. I.e. String for raw text
    O - type of the Output for the model, I.e. Sentiment, for Text->Sentiment extraction
    All Superinterfaces:
    InputAdapter<I>, OutputAdapter<O>, Serializable

    public interface InferenceAdapter<I,O>
extends InputAdapter<I>, OutputAdapter<O>
    This interface describes methods needed to convert custom JVM objects to INDArrays, suitable for feeding neural networks
